description: Coachwhip is a fictional character. She is a supervillain in the Marvel Comics universe, most notably as a member of the Serpent Society.
name: Coachwhip
powers: Wears a polarized strip of material which protects her eyes from bright light
Wields electrically-charged chain-whips attached to gauntlets
Wields electrically-charged steel link whips attached to wristbands
